Key Match Events: Jamal Musiala scored a goal and set up three more in the match
Florian Wirtz scored their third goal after a one-two with Musiala
Kai Havertz scored from the penalty spot in the 81st minute
Pre-Game Insights: All eyes were on Musiala, Wirtz and Havertz ahead of the match as they are expected to lead a new generation in Germany
Former captain Ilkay Gündogan and mainstays and World Cup winners Toni Kroos, Thomas Müller and Manuel Neuer retired from international football
Post-Match Reflections: German celebrations were a reoccuring theme in the Nations League group match
Miscellaneous Highlights: Aleksandar Pavlovic scored his first goal for Germany in the 77th minute
Germany took the lead in the Nations League Group A3 match with Füllkrug's tapping in a Musiala assist in the 27th minute
